##The present is history: There is no reversal

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
February 7,2020.

The 14th day of the first lunar month.

Day 16 of the city closure in Wuhan.

The 15th day of the closing of Heaven's gate.

I hesitate to reply you, because according to my information and past experience, the so-called rescue, mostly for the means of smoke public opinion. It's not that I don't believe in miracles, it's that I've been punched in the face too many times. Experience and intuition tell me: There is no reversal. You said you didn't know him or see him, but you really felt bad. I completely understand. You weren't the only one who was upset last night, and everyone with a conscience and a heart is as upset as you are. Because we experienced an ordinary like you and me, ordinary people, gentle and professional doctor, friends, son, husband, father for our suffering.

Ten years ago, as a cynic, I naively wrote in my review of the Foxconn suicides: "If the death of any body that has nothing to do with us has no effect on us, then obviously our own death will be like grass. ". If we do not respond to the cries of others, one day when we shout, receive, will also be, terrible silence. Life is precious, but there is something more precious than life, and that is the creed that makes life last: one for all, and all for one. Such physical death, whether by suicide or sacrifice, is of value. If foxconn's dozens of deaths can awaken the conscience of its bosses and prompt state owned enterprises to improve the conditions and treatment of their workers, their suicides will undoubtedly be of value. Otherwise, they're cannon fodder. And Cannon Fodder like China is piling up in Mount Everest. I really, really, really don't want us to end up taking it to new heights."

Today I am clear enough to realize that if we can not change anything with this event. The only thing we can do, then, is lose weight, exercise, buy lipstick, eat hot pot, watch a movie, deliver a delivery, run a marathon -- the golden age of being quiet and busy, when faced with multiple choice questions such as exams, working overtime, looking for a job, getting promoted, buying a house, getting married, having children, and emigrating, we can still remember the feeling we felt at 9:30 pm on February 6,2020 because of the suffering of Dr. Li Wenliang.

Can you do that?

Do you understand me?
